<a class="expander" href="#"><strong>How To Refine Your Search</strong></a>
<div class="content">
<p>Use the search options on the left to narrow down your search results. If you don't select any filters, you will see all incentive programs.

Filter categories are Assistance Type, Purpose, Industry, and Agency.

If you select one or more filter terms in one filter category, you will see all incentive programs that match any one of the terms selected.
</p>
</div>

